    {
      "name": "places/ChIJoWx2xJWpQjQRdECjBbw_IkA/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21aTFp6ZDRWVWhGTVRkcFluSkpXV2QzTVd4dFRtYxAB",
      "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 個月前",
      "rating": 4,
      "text": {
        "text": "沒有特別覺得好好吃或不好吃\n就普普通通\n飲料可以喝到飽（飲料機、冰沙機）\n環境還算乾淨\n只是吃完身體會有一點點味道\n\n有提前訂位\n平日19點來差不多滿的",
        "languageCode": "zh-Hant"
      },
